       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. TEST-LOGIN.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY "session.cpy".

       01 WS-REQUIRED-ROLE PIC X(30).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.

       MAIN-PROCEDURE.

           MOVE SPACES TO WS-REQUIRED-ROLE

           CALL "LOGIN" USING APP-SESSION WS-REQUIRED-ROLE

           DISPLAY " "
           DISPLAY "Status    : " FUNCTION TRIM(SESSION-STATUS)
           DISPLAY "Message   : " FUNCTION TRIM(SESSION-MESSAGE)
           DISPLAY "Logged in : " SESSION-LOGGED-IN
           DISPLAY "User ID   : " FUNCTION TRIM(SESSION-USER-ID)
           DISPLAY "Username  : " FUNCTION TRIM(SESSION-USERNAME)
           DISPLAY "Full name : " FUNCTION TRIM(SESSION-FULL-NAME)
           DISPLAY "Role      : " FUNCTION TRIM(SESSION-ROLE)

           STOP RUN.

